{
    "poem_title": "- LXIX - Al conde don Thomas Porcey, mártir en Inglaterra ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Lope de Vega",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Como es la patria celestial colonia,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "bien que el camino a los mortales agro,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "ilustrísimo Conde, a quien consagro",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "los árboles de Apolo y de Tritonia,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Como es la patria celestial colonia,\nbien que el camino a los mortales agro,\nilustrísimo Conde, a quien consagro\nlos árboles de Apolo y de Tritonia,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "fuiste contra la fiera Babilonia,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+----+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "aunque cordero tierno por milagro,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "nuevo, divino, heroico Meleagro",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "de la escocesa Silva Caledonia.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "fuiste contra la fiera Babilonia,\naunque cordero tierno por milagro,\nnuevo, divino, heroico Meleagro\nde la escocesa Silva Caledonia."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Ya muerto, otro Mercurio te contemplo,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+++--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "que tomando las arnas y la espada,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "despojos de tu noble mausoleo,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ya muerto, otro Mercurio te contemplo,\nque tomando las arnas y la espada,\ndespojos de tu noble mausoleo,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "en defensa de Cristo y de su templo,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "Julián y Babilonia derribada,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "confiesen que ha vencido el Galileo.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "en defensa de Cristo y de su templo,\nJulián y Babilonia derribada,\nconfiesen que ha vencido el Galileo."
        }
    ]
}